==In popular media==
* The gallery was seen in &quot;Wolfgang Becker&#x27;s&quot; movie &quot;Goodbye, Lenin!&quot;
* The gallery was featured in the fifth leg of &quot;The Amazing Race 6&quot; and the sixth leg of &quot;The Amazing Race 32&quot;.
